channel.item:
			Version 1.1.1

				<style>
					ul {
						margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 20px;
					}
					li {
						padding: 2px;
					}
				</style>
 				<p>Changes in this version:</p>
 				<ul>
					<li>Improved Reading Recap with styling tweaks, keyboard navigation with arrows, and now always enabled even during a sync.</li>
					<li>Added a Delete menu item in settings to unsubscribe from a feed, in addition to command-delete.</li>
					<li>Fixed unread syncing and sidebar row selection to better track many quick changes.</li>
					<li>Fixed remembering sidebar width position when restarting the app.</li>
				</ul>

			Sun, 29 Mar 2026 19:15:00 -0000

"application/octet-stream" />
			15.0
